# Skybox Front-End Standards

## üéØ Quick Rules

### Naming
- **Components**: `PascalCase.tsx` (EventCard.tsx)
- **CSS Classes**: `kebab-case` (event-card, hero-section)
- **Folders**: Group by feature (`/components/home/`, `/components/events/`)

### Colors (Orange + Green Only)
```css
--primary: 220 70% 35%;        /* MLB Blue */
--secondary: 28 80% 52%;       /* Orange/Amber */
--whatsapp: 142 70% 49%;      /* Single Green */
```

### Responsive Design
- **Mobile-first**: Start with mobile, add `md:` and `lg:` breakpoints
- **Grid**: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- **Typography**: `text-4xl md:text-5xl` for headers

### Component Structure
```tsx
interface ComponentProps {
  title: string;
  className?: string;
}

export const Component: FC<ComponentProps> = ({ title, className = '' }) => {
  return (
    <div className={`base-styles ${className}`}>
      {/* Content */}
    </div>
  );
};
```

### Accessibility
- **Alt text**: All images need descriptive alt text
- **ARIA**: Use `role="article"`, `aria-labelledby`
- **Semantic HTML**: Use `<article>`, `<section>`, `<nav>`

### Performance
- **Images**: Use `loading="lazy"` for below-fold images
- **Animations**: Use `hover-lift`, `glow-on-hover` classes
- **TypeScript**: No `any` types, proper interfaces

